    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Android Annotations @ViewById Generator plugin for Android Studio / IntelliJ IDEA]]></title>
    <link href="http://mrmans0n.github.io/blog/2014/01/12/android-annotations-at-viewbyid-generator-plugin-for-android-studio-slash-intellij-idea/"/>
