    <id>http://mrmans0n.github.io/blog/2014/01/12/android-annotations-at-viewbyid-generator-plugin-for-android-studio-slash-intellij-idea</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>I released a little plugin this week for being used in Android Studio or IntelliJ, for being able to generate automatically the <code>@ViewById</code> annotations from the awesome <a href="http://androidannotations.org">Android Annotations</a>.</p>

<p>You can access the menu by clicking on a layout id like R.layout.your_layout_name, selecting <strong>Generate</strong> and it will be there.</p>

<p><img src="http://mrm.perry.es/viewbyid-intellij-plugin.png" alt="" /></p>

<p>Take a look in <a href="http://plugins.jetbrains.com/plugin/7376">here</a> or look for it in the official IDE repositories.</p>

<p>The project is <a href="https://github.com/mrmans0n/android-viewbyid-generator">open sourced</a>.</p>
